               <item n="m_philcomment_old">&lt;h3&gt;Transliteration&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
&lt;b&gt;a6.&lt;/b&gt; According to [[TochSprR(B)2]]: 64 fn. 2 the reading &lt;i&gt;rāmt&lt;/i&gt; should be corrected to &lt;i&gt;ramt&lt;/i&gt;, and the &lt;i&gt;kroścaṃ&lt;/i&gt; to &lt;i&gt;krośce&lt;/i&gt; in the transcription.&lt;br&gt; 
&lt;b&gt;b1.&lt;/b&gt; According to [[TochSprR(B)2]]: 64 fn. 13 &lt;i&gt;somo añyai&lt;/i&gt; should be read as &lt;i&gt;somw añyai&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;br&gt;
