&lt;b&gt;a8. &lt;/b&gt; Emendation according to TochSprR(B)2: 64 fn. 8.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;General remarks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This leaf immediately follows [[THT 28]]. It belongs to the second part of the Mārgavarga (XII) and includes strophes 9d-21c in a 4x15-syllable-metre (rhythm = 7/8 and 8/7). Contains translation of Uv 12.12-12.13.&lt;/p&gt;</item>
